{"id":2647,"date":"2023-07-08T16:20:15","date_gmt":"2023-07-08T09:20:15","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/?p=2647"},"modified":"2023-09-18T16:20:53","modified_gmt":"2023-09-18T09:20:53","slug":"truong-dai-hoc-thanh-do-tap-huan-phuong-phap-giang-day-tich-cuc-cho-giang-vien-truoc-them-nam-hoc-moi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/truong-dai-hoc-thanh-do-tap-huan-phuong-phap-giang-day-tich-cuc-cho-giang-vien-truoc-them-nam-hoc-moi\/","title":{"rendered":"TR\u01af\u1edcNG \u0110\u1ea0I H\u1eccC TH\u00c0NH \u0110\u00d4 T\u1eacP HU\u1ea4N PH\u01af\u01a0NG PH\u00c1P GI\u1ea2NG D\u1ea0Y T\u00cdCH C\u1ef0C CHO GI\u1ea2NG VI\u00caN TR\u01af\u1edaC TH\u1ec0M N\u0102M H\u1eccC M\u1edaI"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">V\u1edbi v\u1ecb th\u1ebf <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0111\u1ee9ng top 10 c\u00e1c c\u01a1 s\u1edf c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ea1y v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t (x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng 5) trong b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng Private University Ranking: ASEAN, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ea7y v\u00e0 tr\u00f2 nh\u00e0 Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 lu\u00f4n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> n\u00e2ng cao h\u01a1n n\u1eefa ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ea1y v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc. Ng\u00e0y 06\/07 v\u00e0 07\/07, Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c T\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n \u201cPh\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y t\u00edch c\u1ef1c\u201d v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tham gia c\u1ee7a TS. Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00fay V\u00e2n &#8211; Ph\u00f3 Hi\u1ec7u tr\u01b0\u1edfng, PGS.TS. \u0110\u00e0o Th\u1ecb \u00c1i Thi &#8211; Ph\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c Tr\u01b0\u1edfng\/ph\u00f3 Khoa, Gi\u1ea3ng vi\u00ean, Nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16685\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/IMG_3547-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a bu\u1ed5i T\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n, c\u00e1c th\u1ea7y c\u00f4, di\u1ec5n gi\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng nhau th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng cho to\u00e0n th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 gi\u1ea3ng vi\u00ean v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m c\u1ed1t l\u00f5i li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau d\u1ea1y h\u1ecdc, ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p d\u1ea1y h\u1ecdc, hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 n\u1ed9i dung ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o,&#8230; Gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u v\u00e0 l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p h\u1ecfi \u0111\u00e1p, k\u00edch th\u00edch t\u01b0 duy, th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn, l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c nh\u00f3m, tr\u1ef1c quan, b\u1ec3 c\u00e1 v\u00e0ng,&#8230;<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Trong \u0111\u00f3, t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1ea1y c\u1ea7n \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p d\u1ea1y h\u1ecdc hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i theo h\u01b0\u1edbng ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc. C\u00f3 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y c\u1ee7a Tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh t\u1ef1u cao h\u01a1n trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16687\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/IMG_3934-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16693\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/IMG_3843-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">T\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n \u201cPh\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y t\u00edch c\u1ef1c\u201d \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf ra b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t l\u1edbn trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p d\u1ea1y v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc trong n\u0103m h\u1ecdc m\u1edbi 2022-2023. Tin ch\u1eafc r\u1eb1ng, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 nghi\u00eam t\u00fac n\u00e0y, Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 s\u1ebd s\u1edbm n\u00e2ng cao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y, ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u l\u1edbp sinh vi\u00ean k\u1ebf c\u1eadn v\u1eefng chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng lao \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16689\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/IMG_3966-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng cho vi\u1ec7c th\u1ea7y v\u00e0 tr\u00f2 nh\u00e0 Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng n\u00e2ng cao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 gi\u1ea3ng vi\u00ean, t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c c\u00e1c l\u1edbp t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n, t\u1ea1o m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n h\u1ecdc thu\u1eadt \u0111a d\u1ea1ng cho gi\u1ea3ng vi\u00ean v\u00e0 sinh vi\u00ean. Hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng, v\u1edbi l\u1ea7n n\u00e2ng cao nghi\u1ec7p v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c th\u1ea7y c\u00f4 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam cho m\u00ecnh nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p, kinh nghi\u1ec7m, h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o sinh vi\u00ean d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>V\u1edbi v\u1ecb th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ee9ng top 10 c\u00e1c c\u01a1 s\u1edf c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ea1y v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t (x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng 5) trong b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng Private University Ranking: ASEAN, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ea7y v\u00e0 tr\u00f2 nh\u00e0 Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 lu\u00f4n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng n\u00e2ng cao h\u01a1n n\u1eefa ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":5,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[1],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2647"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/5"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2647"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2647\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":2648,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2647\/revisions\/2648"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2647"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2647"},{"taxonomy":"post_